40:13.912 --> 40:16.548
Daniel:
WHAT IS A CONSCIENCE?

40:16.582 --> 40:22.554
IS IT SOMETHING WE CAN LOCATE
ON AN MRI?

40:22.588 --> 40:24.389
STUDIES HAVE SHOWN

40:24.422 --> 40:27.526
THAT PEOPLE WITH DAMAGE TO THE
VENTROMEDIAL PREFRONTAL CORTEX

40:27.559 --> 40:31.463
ARE ACTUALLY MORE WILLING
TO SACRIFICE A HUMAN LIFE

40:31.497 --> 40:36.968
AS LONG AS THEY PERCEIVE THAT
IT'S FOR SOME GREATER GOOD.

40:37.002 --> 40:39.738
