40:53.284 --> 40:56.121
OR ARE WE BETTER OFF
SPENDING EVERY WAKING MOMENT

40:56.154 --> 40:59.457
TENDING OUR OWN SELFISH NEEDS?

40:59.491 --> 41:00.926
THE GOOD NEWS IS,

41:00.959 --> 41:03.361
IT TURNS OUT THERE'S
AN EVOLUTIONARY ADVANTAGE

41:03.394 --> 41:05.196
TO SIMPLE HUMAN KINDNESS.

41:05.230 --> 41:07.198
WE COULDN'T GET THROUGH
A COLD PALEOLITHIC WINTER

41:07.232 --> 41:09.501
WITHOUT A LITTLE COOPERATION.

41:09.535 --> 41:14.506
STILL, ON SOME PREHISTORIC LEVEL
WE'RE ALL LONE HUNTERS.

41:14.540 --> 41:17.509
SO IT CAN FEEL DANGEROUS
TO SHOW ANY SOFTNESS

41:17.543 --> 41:19.645
TO OTHER MEMBERS OF THE TRIBE.

41:25.283 --> 41:28.286
BUT IF WE MANAGE TO LAY DOWN OUR
CLUBS AND OUR SHARPENED ROCKS,

41:28.319 --> 41:33.592
ANSWERING THE CALL
OF THE ALTRUISTIC IMPERATIVE

41:33.625 --> 41:36.361
CAN BE ITS OWN REWARD.
